title: Antergos 2014-08-07 (64bit)
description:
OS Type: Linux | Based on: Arch | Category: Desktop, Live Medium

Antergos is a modern, elegant and powerful operating system,
based on Arch Linux.

It started life under the name of Cinnarch, combining the Cinnamon
desktop with the Arch Linux distribution, but the project has moved
on from its original goals and now offers a choice of several desktops:

- Cinnamon
- MATE
- Xfce
- Gnome
- KDE
- LXDE
- Razor-qt
- Enlightenment
